# Agent Rules

This project is a Monorepo using Bun Workspaces.

## Project Structure
- `packages/backend`: The backend API (Hono, Postgres).
- `packages/frontend`: The frontend application (React, React Router).

## Navigation
- Always check `package.json` in directories to understand available scripts.
- Use `bun run` for scripts.

## Style
- Use TypeScript for all new code.
- Prefer functional components for React.
